The police have reported that the suspect responsible for the attack is a presumed militant of Daesh (ISIL).
They have discovered that the functioning of the Sun is based on the same basic principles as the other stars: the activity of all the stars in the solar system is determined only by their luminosity and rotation.
The luminosity is used together with the rotation to define the Rossby number of a star, which is related to the plasma flow.
The lower the Rossby number, the lower the activity of the star with respect to the magnetic inversions.
